from matplotlib.colors import ListedColormap

def plot_separating_surface(X, y, cls, view_support=False):
    x_min = min(X[:, 0]) - 0.1
    x_max = max(X[:, 0]) + 0.1
    y_min = min(X[:, 1]) - 0.1
    y_max = max(X[:, 1]) + 0.1
    h = 0.005
    cm = plt.cm.RdBu
    cm_bright = ListedColormap(['#FF0000', '#0000FF'])

    xx, yy = np.meshgrid(np.arange(x_min, x_max, h),
                             np.arange(y_min, y_max, h))
    Z = cls.predict(np.c_[xx.ravel(), yy.ravel()])

    plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8))
    plt.scatter(X[:, 0], X[:, 1], c=y, edgecolors='k', s=40, cmap=cm_bright)
    if view_support:
        plt.scatter(X[cls.support_, 0], X[cls.support_, 1],
                    c=y[cls.support_], edgecolors='k', s=150, cmap=cm_bright)
    Z = Z.reshape(xx.shape)
    plt.contourf(xx, yy, Z, cmap=cm, alpha=.3)
    plt.title(" ", size=15)
    plt.xlabel(r'$x_1$', size=15)
    plt.ylabel(r'$x_2$', size=15)

from sklearn.compose import ColumnTransformer
from sklearn.preprocessing import OneHotEncoder
from sklearn.pipeline import Pipeline

column_transformer = ColumnTransformer([
    ('ohe', OneHotEncoder(), categorical),
    ('scaling', StandardScaler(), numeric_features)
])

pipeline = Pipeline(steps=[
    ('ohe', column_transformer),
    ('classification', LogisticRegression(solver='lbfgs', max_iter=200))
])

model = pipeline.fit(X_train.drop(columns=["Date"]), y_train)
y_pred = model.predict_proba(X_test.drop(columns=["Date"]))[:, 1]
print("Test logloss = %.4f" % log_loss(y_test, y_pred))
print("Test roc auc score = %.4f" % roc_auc_score(y_test, y_pred))

In [43]:
Xtr, Xval, ytr, yval = train_test_split(
    X_train.drop(columns=["Date"]), y_train, test_size=0.2, stratify=y_train, random_state=42
)

candidates = {
    "lbfgs_C1": LogisticRegression(solver="lbfgs", penalty="l2", C=1.0, max_iter=300),
    "lbfgs_C3": LogisticRegression(solver="lbfgs", penalty="l2", C=3.0, max_iter=300),
    "saga_elastic_C3": LogisticRegression(solver="saga", penalty="elasticnet",
                                          l1_ratio=0.2, C=3.0, max_iter=300, n_jobs=-1),
}

results = {}
for name, clf in candidates.items():
    pipe = Pipeline(steps=[('ohe', column_transformer), ('classification', clf)])
    pipe.fit(Xtr, ytr)
    p_val = pipe.predict_proba(Xval)[:, 1]
    auc_val = roc_auc_score(yval, p_val)
    ll_val = log_loss(yval, p_val)
    results[name] = (auc_val, ll_val)
    print(f"{name}: val AUC={auc_val:.4f} | val logloss={ll_val:.4f}")

best_name = max(results, key=lambda k: results[k][0])
best_clf = candidates[best_name]
print("Best by val AUC:", best_name)

pipeline = Pipeline(steps=[('ohe', column_transformer), ('classification', best_clf)])
model = pipeline.fit(X_train.drop(columns=["Date"]), y_train)

y_pred = model.predict_proba(X_test.drop(columns=["Date"]))[:, 1]
print("Test logloss = %.4f" % log_loss(y_test, y_pred))
print("Test roc auc score = %.4f" % roc_auc_score(y_test, y_pred))
